            h5 Nicholas Dominguez

            p.text-light
              | What can I say, I am your friendly neighborhood web developer. I love to make apps that help others do their work easier and maybe one day I will become a Jedi like my father before me. 

            a(href='../about') Learn More â†’

            ul.social-links.round
              li
                a.icon(href="https://twitter.com/NicDominguez")
                  img(src="/static/images/svg/twitter_icon.svg")
              li
                a.icon(href="https://github.com/NicDominguez")
                  img(src="/static/images/svg/github_icon.svg")
              li
                a.icon(href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/nicdominguez/")
                  img(src="/static/images/svg/linkedin_icon.svg")

